  "guideSwipeItem2": "Swipe up to send a Priority Connect (uses coins).",
  "guideSwipeItem3": "Swipe down to Explore Next and skip a profile for now.",
  "guideSwipeItem4": "You can switch between swipe and grid mode using the toggle icon in the top bar.",
  "guideGridTitle": "Grid View",
  "guideGridItem1": "Browse profiles in a grid layout for a quick overview.",
  "guideGridItem2": "Tap on a profile image to reveal the four action buttons: Connect, Priority Connect, Nope, and Explore Next.",
  "guideGridItem3": "Long press on a profile image to see their details without opening the full profile.",
  "guideConnectionsTitle": "Connecting with People",
  "guideConnectionsItem1": "When two people Connect with each other, it's a match!",
  "guideConnectionsItem2": "After matching, you can start chatting right away.",
  "guideConnectionsItem3": "Use Priority Connect to stand out and increase your chances.",
  "guideConnectionsItem4": "Check the Exchanges tab to see all your matches and conversations.",
  "guideChatTitle": "Chat & Messaging",
  "guideChatItem1": "Send text messages, photos, and voice notes.",
  "guideChatItem2": "Use the translation feature to chat in different languages.",
  "guideChatItem3": "Open chat settings to customize your experience: toggle grammar check, smart replies, cultural tips, word breakdown, pronunciation help, and more.",
  "guideChatItem4": "Enable text-to-speech to hear translations, show language flags, and track your language learning XP.",
  "guideFiltersTitle": "Discovery Filters",
  "guideFiltersItem1": "Tap the filter icon to set your preferences: age range, distance, languages, and more.",
  "guideFiltersItem2": "Random Mode: enable this toggle to discover random people from all over the world, sorted by distance. Each refresh gives you a new set of profiles. When Random Mode is off, only people close to you are shown. You can also select specific countries to narrow your search.",
  "guideFiltersItem3": "Filters help you find people who match what you're looking for. You can adjust them anytime.",
  "guideTravelTitle": "Travel & Explore",
  "guideTravelItem1": "Activate Traveler Mode to appear in discovery for a city you plan to visit for 24 hours.",
  "guideTravelItem2": "Local Guides can help travelers discover their city and culture.",
  "guideTravelItem3": "Language exchange partners are matched based on what you speak and what you want to learn.",
  "guideMembershipTitle": "Base Membership",
  "guideMembershipItem1": "Your base membership gives you access to all core features: swiping, chatting, and matching.",
  "guideMembershipItem2": "Membership starts with a free trial after your first sign-up.",
  "guideMembershipItem3": "When your membership expires, you can renew it to continue using the app.",
  "guideTiersTitle": "VIP Tiers (Silver, Gold, Platinum)",
  "guideTiersItem1": "Silver: Get more daily connects, see who connected with you, and priority support.",
  "guideTiersItem2": "Gold: Everything in Silver plus unlimited connects, advanced filters, and read receipts.",
  "guideTiersItem3": "Platinum: Everything in Gold plus profile boost, top picks, and exclusive features.",
  "guideTiersItem4": "VIP tiers are independent from your base membership and provide extra perks.",
  "guideCoinsTitle": "Coins",
  "guideCoinsItem1": "Coins are used for premium actions. Here are the costs:",
  "guideCoinsItem2": "• Priority Connect: 10 coins  • Boost: 50 coins  • Direct Message: 50 coins",
  "guideCoinsItem3": "• Incognito: 30 coins/day  • Traveler: 100 coins/day",
  "guideCoinsItem4": "• Listen (TTS): 5 coins  • Grid Extend: 10 coins  • Learning Coach: 10 coins/session",
  "guideCoinsItem5": "You receive 20 free coins daily. Earn more through achievements, leaderboard rankings, and the Shop.",
  "guideLeaderboardTitle": "Leaderboard",
  "guideLeaderboardItem1": "Compete with other users to climb the leaderboard and earn rewards.",
  "guideLeaderboardItem2": "Earn points by being active, completing your profile, and engaging with others.",
  "guideGridFiltersTitle": "Grid Filters",
  "guideGridFiltersItem1": "In grid mode, use the filter chips at the top to narrow down profiles.",
  "guideGridFiltersItem2": "All: Shows everyone in your discovery pool.",
  "guideGridFiltersItem3": "Connected: People you sent a Connect to.",
  "guideGridFiltersItem4": "Priority: People you sent a Priority Connect to.",
  "guideGridFiltersItem5": "Passed: People you chose to pass on.",
  "guideGridFiltersItem6": "Explored: People you skipped without deciding yet — you can revisit them later.",
  "guideGridFiltersItem7": "Matches: People you mutually Connected with (both said Let's Connect).",
  "guideGridFiltersItem8": "My Network: All people you're connected with — includes Matches and accepted Priority Connects.",
  "guideGridFiltersItem9": "Travelers: People with Traveler Mode active, visiting a city near you.",
  "guideGridFiltersItem10": "Guides: Local Guides ready to help travelers discover their city.",
  "guideGridFiltersItem11": "You can combine multiple filters at once to refine your search.",
  "guideExchangesTitle": "Exchanges (Chat)",
  "guideExchangesItem1": "Exchanges is where all your conversations live. You'll find it in the bottom menu.",
  "guideExchangesItem2": "The red badge on the Exchanges icon shows the number of conversations with unread messages or pending approvals.",
  "guideExchangesItem3": "Use the filter chips to organize your chats: All, New, Unread, Favorites, To Approve, Matches, and Direct.",
  "guideExchangesItem4": "New and Unread show conversations with messages you haven't read yet. The filter chip shows the count when greater than 0.",
  "guideExchangesItem5": "To Approve shows Priority Connect requests waiting for your decision. Accept or reject them directly from the list.",
  "guideExchangesItem6": "Unread conversations are highlighted with bold text and a gold shimmer effect so you can spot them easily.",
  "guideExchangesItem7": "Tap a conversation to open the chat. Once opened, it's marked as read and the badge count decreases.",
  "guideExchangesItem8": "Long press a conversation for more options. Use the star icon to add a chat to your Favorites.",
  "guideExchangesItem9": "Each conversation shows the other user's language flags, so you know what languages they speak.",
